"content": "<h2>Flint tools</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:2-Josh5:3\">JOS 5:2–5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:25\">EXO 4:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:1\">JER 17:1</a></p>\n<h2>Flinty rock</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:9\">JOB 28:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:13-Deut32:14\">DEU 32:13–32:14</a></p>\n<h2>Metaphorical use of flint</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:9\">EZK 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:28\">ISA 5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:7\">ISA 50:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:12</a></p>",
